      "category": "team",
      "content": "Secondary clients such as LINE for Windows/Mac require 2FA at first login. However, due to insufficient verification logic on the server-side, the attacker was able to bypass 2FA after the attacker succeeds QR login by tricking the victim to click a specially crafted URL.",
